   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Fourth year of Antoninus Caesar, our lord, Epeiph 28. Mystes, son of Akousilaos and grandson of Horos, has paid to Artem( ), collector of money taxes  at Memphis, for the poll tax incumbent on unskilled workers (?) in the same year, eight drachmas including the extra charge, i. e 8 dr."</ab>
         </div>
